{"tid":1449354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:53:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:56:57.000Z","uid":56138,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1bfcc246ce2a0bddbd37c8701f879786116a09c7","tid":1449354,"uid":56138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:53:01.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpt6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=ebb53a8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpt6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=308ed7c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"36cc7beac89aab1dadd44d55a90e57db5f3856ff","tid":1449354,"uid":46761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:54:43.000Z","msg":"黑衣黑褲黑衫眼罩口罩<br />\n機場見 (野餐）"},{"pid":"9b2045125909cca5ac1a7856569b2259683ba138","tid":1449354,"uid":216685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:55:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab3b3765c07a41f25f371f604557d5f22ce70ea7","tid":1449354,"uid":92476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:55:40.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">內有機場抗爭策略及方案：<